column3: Need to play the way you're facing when under pressure
All the way to the line on goal kicks
Many players tentative on defense, not working hard to recover; exception is Jorge consistently taking nice angled positions to cover outside defenders
On their goal, defense and mid fielders on left side not anticipating to get back
Goalkeeper stays on the line when ball is in other half
When getting the ball with time, don't just kick it
Goalkeeper not using hands cost us a goal
Lots of standing and watching, not working hard enough off the ball
